@startuml leaver_killswitch_flow
title Leaver / Kill-Switch Flow
actor "HR System" as HR
participant "Identity\nGovernance" as IGA
participant "EntraID" as EID
participant "Intune MDM" as MDM
participant "ServiceNow" as SN
database "Audit Log" as LOG

HR -> IGA : Termination event
IGA -> EID : Disable account (< 2 min)
IGA -> MDM : Wipe corporate devices
IGA -> SN : Create offboarding ticket
EID --> LOG : Account disabled event
MDM --> LOG : Device wipe confirmed
SN --> HR : Offboarding checklist
IGA -> EID : Revoke all tokens
EID --> LOG : Token revocation event
@enduml
